en.title: Ade Rai Wearing QP at Gold Gym, Jakarta.
en.content:
FE's Indonesian Spokesman, Ade Rai, Champion World Class Bodybuilder and Celebrity, seen here wearing FE's Quantum Pendant with FE Presidential Director, KC Phoon, Ade's wife, Kenny Amelia and Ade's PA, Halim Hsiang at one of Ade's Gold Gyms in Jakarta. Ade is very popular in Indonesia where he has his own radio talk show and writes a column in the Jakarta Post on health and fitness. Ade is frequently featured on TV, magazines and the newspapers.
FE is honoured to have Ade Rai as FE's Spokesman for Indonesia!
